Dialogs.Dialog: 高嶺
Ah, this is an open area for recreation... This looks fun♪
Okay then, where we should start?
高嶺
All of the attractions seem to be fun... Hey, don't get lost, okay?
Okay then, let's see...
高嶺
Look, this is another dating spot♪
Okay! Let's get pumped today!
高嶺
Fufu, didn't you get a lot of fun yet? Me neither!
Okay, let's have more fun today.
高嶺
Very well, I'll go with.
Thank you. Well then, one more time!
高嶺
Knot 30 was interesting. Do you think it might have been a mental exercise?
You might be right, I think it was a fun rush.
高嶺
You know, I have been thinking... Knot 30 must have a way to go through it.
I think you're right, but what would that be...
高嶺
It's so nostalgic to play "Daruma-san is falling". I remember playing it when I was little.
I think I played other kinds of games when I was little.
高嶺
Daruma-san is going to fall... Does Daruma-san never fall?
Hmm?... Now that I think about it, why is it called like that?
高嶺
It's fun to split watermelons. It's a little scary, though.
Well, I think the person who splits it looks happy.
高嶺
The word watermelon is written as "west melon". What about the southern melon?
Huh?... Ah, that'll be a pumpkin!
高嶺
Catching marshmallows won't work without the two us breathing together.
It might just be like doubles in tennis.
高嶺
It seems that the ingredients from the marshmallows were used by foreign kings as throat medicine.
Really? Well, of course I knew that.
高嶺
Don't you feel a little more grown-up when you play darts?
Certainly, darts give that kind of vibe.
高嶺
The pro darts player has taken my darts. I might miss them a little later.
Haha, don't be like that, you'll play too.
高嶺
I feel tension in the air, similar to high speed. It's similar to the one I like when playing cards.
You're right ▲高嶺＊＊▲. And it seems you're good at it...
高嶺
I was remembering the speed... And it seems that calling cards "toranpu" is a Japan-only thing, isn't it?
Huh, I do wonder how they call cards in other countries.
高嶺
It's so fascinating when you look at soap bubbles soaring in the sky...
I never knew you were such a romantic ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
高嶺
I really want to get inside a big soap bubble. Do you think that sounds funny?
Haha, I think that it'll look good on you ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
高嶺
The game we were playing before was so interesting! However, I think it'll be strange for lovers to compete against each other.
Hmm, if you put it that way... But I think it's fun.
高嶺
For this game, you first have to win the rock-paper-scissors game. I have to carefully read the patterns...
Don't you think it's better to compete with reflexes rather than thinking too much about it?
高嶺
This is a battle of the minds. It's fun to outwit other people♪
Don't burn yourself with the bargains.
高嶺
What country created this kind of game?
Let's see... Isn't that from a Japanese TV show? It looks like it.
高嶺
This was interesting, but I feel the aliens might be sad.
You think you? I don't feel like doing anything anymore.
高嶺
Fufu. What would you do if an alien really attacked you?
If that happens... I will protect you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲!
高嶺
The key here is how to choose a panel, isn't it? If you let your guard down, it won't work at all.
I think it might be a good idea to go by intuition.
高嶺
I want to connect a lot of panels and get a lot of medals.
Oh, I see you're getting pretty serious.
高嶺
You can have as many slots as the number of tickets you have with you, while we're on a date.
It may come in handy to aim for that.
高嶺
I'm sorry about the jackpot before. You were so close to get it.
When I remember that, I feel some frustration. But we'll get it next time!
高嶺
My heart went "Banzai!" when you took the jackpot before.
It was all thanks to your support, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
高嶺
Grand Cross was interesting. I really like music tours♪
It was like an amusement park, and it was fun just to watch it.
高嶺
It was such a pity, you almost had the Grand Cross jackpot.
The way they did the showcase was amazing, and I wanted to see how it looked when I achieved the jackpot...
高嶺
Congrats on taking the jackpot. It was so lively, like being in a country of dreams♪
I felt like I was in a theme park.
高嶺
I want to travel around world heritage sites someday, like Fortune Trinity♪
Haha, I feel it'll be a great adventure.
高嶺
It was a pity not achieving the Fortune trinity's jackpot... My hands are still sweaty.
It would have been great if we could have get it... *Sigh*.
高嶺
I'm really excited for the Grand Cross jackpot♪ The medals are pouring down are like a waterfall.
I got the treasure!
高嶺
Animalotta looks so funny. Anima is so cute▼
I think it was fun too, also the game was well done.
高嶺
It was such a pity not obtaining the jackpot at Animalotta. Even thought a lot of balls fell...
It all was over before I realized I was only looking at the roulette lights...
高嶺
The lights from Animalotta, when you got the jackpot, were amazing!
It was like a festival of lights and sounds.
高嶺
It's fun when you have a chance to score the jackpot, even if I get it or not.
I think it's great too, since you get a lot of opportunities.
高嶺
The most exciting time is when you have a chance to score the jackpot. I get disappointed otherwise.
That's the turning point for the game. We should take our chances next time!
高嶺
Your face was so bright when you scored the jackpot♪
Ah, were you looking at me? Haha.
高嶺
People around you couldn't take their eyes off you when you scored the jackpot.
Really? I didn't realize it.
高嶺
There are a lot of medal games, so you can't keep your eyes on each of them, right?
Very well, let's try another medal game!
高嶺
Medal games are interesting and beautiful... and fun♪
Haha, you're hooked on them, aren't you?
高嶺
Look, look over there. A lot of sparkling medals!
I'm satisfied just by playing, but I'm happy when I get a lot of medals.
高嶺
It was fun♪ I hope we can get a lot of medals next time.
Of course, let's come again and get a lot more. It's fun to play together.
高嶺
I had a lot of fun today♪ Did you enjoy yourself too?
Of course, it was so much fun!
高嶺
Fufu. You had a lot of fun playing, didn't you?
It's looks like you did too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
高嶺
Time goes by so quickly when I'm playing games with you.
That only means we are enjoying ourselves.
高嶺
It's been quite some time since I've played this much♪ It was really fun.
Haha, it was refreshing seeing you like that.
高嶺
Every game is fun when I'm with you...
That's because it's exciting when we play together.
高嶺
Do you promise we'll come back again?
If you're asking me, ▲高嶺＊＊▲, then I can't deny your wishes.
高嶺
I have to finish this before... Hey, when do you want to come back?
When? I hope soon, I had a lot of fun.
高嶺
This is so frustrating... Let's come again and try it one more time. I'll do my best then.
It seems you didn't like to loose... I'll do my best next time, too.
高嶺
I made some mistakes back there... I really thought I could do better.
Yes, I'm so frustrated... I'll have my revenge next time.
高嶺
I think I can do it better next time. I feel like I've got the hang of it.
Cool, then we'll have to come back one of these days.
Alright, I'll try my luck.
I got silver? I need to do something about it...
Oh, I got a golden scratch! Yay!
Oh, a platinum scratch... Now I want to get a higher price!
This is the legendary premier scratch! This might be something amazing.
高嶺
Isn't this right, somehow?
高嶺
Pick your left here! I think it's the right move!
高嶺
I feel things might get a little awkward by the middle.
高嶺
Okay, lemme see... They all seem possible to me, I don't really know what to pick.
高嶺
Can I leave it to you?
高嶺
I believe in you.
Now that's more like it!
It's amazing... You were right from the start, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Yay, I got it! This was possible thanks to ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s support!
Ah... I lost.
...I'm sorry, I didn't listen to your advise.
